WEBVTT

00:00.504 --> 00:02.739
<i>Previously on
AMC's Mad Men...</i>

00:02.940 --> 00:04.027
This was my father.

00:04.165 --> 00:06.087
My mother was a 23
year old prostitute

00:06.216 --> 00:08.295
who died having me.

00:08.775 --> 00:09.592
Lucky Strike.

00:09.816 --> 00:11.368
The shot of our lives.

00:11.560 --> 00:13.567
- Tell me what you think.
- I think you are the client,

00:13.696 --> 00:14.728
you should do what you want.

00:14.942 --> 00:18.831
The lost of Jai Alai makes
Lucky Strike 71% of our billings.

00:18.960 --> 00:20.575
You said you'd always come home.

00:20.695 --> 00:21.991
Did you make him leave?

00:22.095 --> 00:23.407
I wanna take you
in that bedroom

00:23.536 --> 00:25.512
and give you a go around
like you've never had.

00:26.944 --> 00:27.737
When are you moving out?

00:27.944 --> 00:29.665
We haven't found the
right place for the kids.

