you can't do anything.

42:24.148 --> 42:25.812
He won't respect you.

42:25.880 --> 42:29.044
What if I don't know?

42:29.112 --> 42:31.642
Well, you can't lead him on.

42:31.710 --> 42:33.775
That is physically
very uncomfortable.

42:33.843 --> 42:35.541
It's not a joke.

42:54.423 --> 42:57.592
did you enjoy the
fuhrer's birthday?

42:57.660 --> 42:59.194
may he live for
a thousand years.

43:01.865 --> 43:04.366
Oh, my father used to say
this is the greatest job
in the world

43:04.434 --> 43:06.368
Except for one thing...
the clients.

43:16.178 --> 43:19.146
Good morning.

43:19.213 --> 43:20.279
Did you make it home
last night?

43:20.347 --> 43:22.813
I did.
