43:25.280 --> 43:27.446
Come inside.

43:30.648 --> 43:32.882
- What's all this?
- For your children.

43:32.949 --> 43:34.450
I bought them the other day,

43:34.517 --> 43:36.118
But I finally got them wrapped.

43:37.386 --> 43:38.686
Thank you.

43:38.754 --> 43:40.488
Want me to get the door?

43:40.555 --> 43:42.256
No.

43:42.324 --> 43:44.691
Do you need some coffee?

43:44.759 --> 43:46.526
I had some.

43:46.593 --> 43:48.293
It was quite a party.

43:49.896 --> 43:52.530
- I really overdid it.
- Me too.

43:56.000 --> 43:58.100
I, uh...

44:01.303 --> 44:03.203
Thank you for bringing my keys.

44:03.271 --> 44:06.206
I really appreciate it.

44:06.274 --> 44:08.108
