to say thank you
for bringing my keys.

44:22.192 --> 44:24.127
Okay.

44:26.730 --> 44:30.467
I know we talked about
how tough things are
for the firm,

44:32.402 --> 44:35.004
But I wanted you to know...

44:38.274 --> 44:41.642
